description: Manage shared access keys of a partner namespace.

commands.name: az eventgrid partner namespace key list
commands.summary: List shared access keys of a partner namespace.
commands.syntax:
az eventgrid partner namespace key list --partner-namespace-name
                                        --resource-group
examples: az eventgrid partner namespace key list --partner-namespace-name MyNamespace --resource-group MyResourceGroup

commands.name: az eventgrid partner namespace key regenerate
commands.summary: Regenerate a shared access key of a partner namespace.
commands.syntax:
az eventgrid partner namespace key regenerate --key-name
                                              --partner-namespace-name
                                              --resource-group
